### BoTCoin API — HTTP request collection
### REST Client for VS Code — covers all endpoints in the project.
### The @job_id / @auto_job_id variables are captured automatically from the submit responses.

@host = http://localhost:8000
@token = your-api-token-here

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# STATUS
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [ST-1] Bot status (paused flag + last run time)
GET {{host}}/status
X-Api-Token: {{token}}

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# MARKET
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [MK-1] All pairs
GET {{host}}/market
X-Api-Token: {{token}}

###

### [MK-2] Single pair
GET {{host}}/market/XBTEUR
X-Api-Token: {{token}}

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# POSITIONS
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [POS-1] All open positions
GET {{host}}/positions
X-Api-Token: {{token}}

###

### [POS-2] Single pair position
GET {{host}}/positions/XBTEUR
X-Api-Token: {{token}}

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# BALANCE
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [BAL-1] Current balance
GET {{host}}/balance
X-Api-Token: {{token}}

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CONTROL
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [CTL-1] Pause the bot
POST {{host}}/control/pause
X-Api-Token: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "updated_by": "manual"
}

###

### [CTL-2] Resume the bot
POST {{host}}/control/resume
X-Api-Token: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "updated_by": "manual"
}

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# BACKTEST
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [BT-1] Full history — recompute path
POST {{host}}/backtest
X-Api-Token: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pair": "XBTEUR",
  "fee_pct": 0.4
}

###

### [BT-2] Live calibration cache (use_live_config=true)
### Requires the scheduler to have run calculate_trading_parameters at least once.
### Falls through to recompute if the cache is cold — result is identical data.
POST {{host}}/backtest
X-Api-Token: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pair": "XBTEUR",
  "fee_pct": 0.4,
  "use_live_config": true
}

###

### [BT-3] Date-sliced — forces the slice + recompute path
POST {{host}}/backtest
X-Api-Token: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pair": "XBTEUR",
  "fee_pct": 0.4,
  "start": "2026-05-20",
  "end": "2026-06-01"
}

###

### [BT-4] Capped at 10 operations
POST {{host}}/backtest
X-Api-Token: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pair": "XBTEUR",
  "fee_pct": 0.4,
  "max_ops": 10
}

###

### [BT-5] ETHEUR pair
POST {{host}}/backtest
X-Api-Token: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pair": "ETHEUR",
  "fee_pct": 0.4
}

###

### [BT-6] Unknown pair → 400
POST {{host}}/backtest
X-Api-Token: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pair": "DOGEEUR"
}

###

### [BT-7] No auth → 401
POST {{host}}/backtest
Content-Type: application/json

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# OPTIMIZER — OPTIMIZE mode
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [OPT-1] Submit — OPTIMIZE mode
# @name submitJob
POST {{host}}/optimizer/jobs
X-Api-Token: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pair": "XBTEUR",
  "mode": "OPTIMIZE",
  "fee_pct": 0.4,
  "train_split": 0.8,
  "n_trials": 1000,
  "seed": 42
}

###

@job_id = {{submitJob.response.body.job_id}}

### [OPT-2] Poll job status (repeat until status != "running")
GET {{host}}/optimizer/jobs/{{job_id}}
X-Api-Token: {{token}}

###

### [OPT-3] Submit while [OPT-1] is still running → 409 Conflict
POST {{host}}/optimizer/jobs
X-Api-Token: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pair": "XBTEUR",
  "mode": "OPTIMIZE"
}

###

### [OPT-4] List all jobs (default limit=20)
GET {{host}}/optimizer/jobs
X-Api-Token: {{token}}

###

### [OPT-5] List with explicit limit
GET {{host}}/optimizer/jobs?limit=5
X-Api-Token: {{token}}

###

### [OPT-6] Get unknown job → 404
GET {{host}}/optimizer/jobs/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
X-Api-Token: {{token}}

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# OPTIMIZER — CURRENT mode
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [OPT-7] CURRENT mode — evaluates the live .env config, returns 1 trial
POST {{host}}/optimizer/jobs
X-Api-Token: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pair": "XBTEUR",
  "mode": "CURRENT",
  "fee_pct": 0.4,
  "train_split": 0.8
}

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# OPTIMIZER — AUTO mode
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [OPT-8] AUTO mode — all defaults (n_trials=1000 initial, max_trials=9000)
# @name submitAutoJob
POST {{host}}/optimizer/jobs
X-Api-Token: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pair": "XBTEUR",
  "mode": "AUTO",
  "fee_pct": 0.4,
  "train_split": 0.8
}

###

@auto_job_id = {{submitAutoJob.response.body.job_id}}

### [OPT-9] Poll AUTO job status (repeat until status != "running")
GET {{host}}/optimizer/jobs/{{auto_job_id}}
X-Api-Token: {{token}}

###

### [OPT-10] AUTO mode — quick smoke (500 initial, max 1000)
POST {{host}}/optimizer/jobs
X-Api-Token: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pair": "XBTEUR",
  "mode": "AUTO",
  "fee_pct": 0.4,
  "train_split": 0.8,
  "n_trials": 500,
  "trial_step": 500,
  "max_trials": 1000,
  "n_seeds": 3,
  "min_agree": 2
}

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# OPTIMIZER — error cases
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [OPT-11] Unknown pair → 400
POST {{host}}/optimizer/jobs
X-Api-Token: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pair": "DOGEEUR",
  "mode": "OPTIMIZE"
}

###

### [OPT-12] n_trials out of range → 422 Unprocessable Entity
POST {{host}}/optimizer/jobs
X-Api-Token: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pair": "XBTEUR",
  "mode": "OPTIMIZE",
  "n_trials": 0
}

###

### [OPT-13] Invalid mode → 422
POST {{host}}/optimizer/jobs
X-Api-Token: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pair": "XBTEUR",
  "mode": "BADMODE"
}

###
